• Alaska Airlines serves all 5 L.A. area airports, 3 Bay Area
airports, San Diego and Palm Springs. Alaska Airlines offers 9
flights between Los Angeles Int'l and Seattle and 8 flights from
Seattle to San Francisco Int'l every business day.
• Next trip, experience the comforts of the Alaska Airlines Board
Room. Our exclusive airport club rooms are conveniently located
in San Francisco, Los Angeles*, Portland, Seattle and Anchorage.
Call 1-800-654-5669 or stop by any Board Room for membership
information.
*Opening late 1992. Prior to opening, Board Room members may use TWA's
Ambassador Club.
• Beginning September 11— Alaska Airlines will provide new Jet
service between Anchorage and Kodiak that will complement the
five flights currently operated by Era Aviation for Alaska Airlines.
Effective October 5, 1992, Alaska Airlines will begin Jet service
between Anchorage and both Aniak and Saint Mary's.
• Plan your sunshine vacation now! Alaska Airlines flies to Mazatlan,
Puerto Vallarta, Los Cabos, and Guadalajara in Mexico; and Palm
Springs, San Diego, Phoenix and Tucson.
Call Your Travel Agent or Alaska Airlines
Vacations at 1-800-468-2248 for informa-
tion on the following vacations:
• Mexico Vacations
• Disneyland and Hollywood Vacations
• San Francisco and Napa Valley Vacations
• San Diego Vacations
• Seattle and Alaska Weekends
